_nc_ohc=DT9Z75OuccgQ7kNvgG47JU4&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCAsU30NH1boiJTcpuPwYUmU52_5mImEt9qhxCdhwRXCA&oe=670A58A5"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "RGP_StoreTrailer_Thumbnail.png", "id": "1394736561278402", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982698_1394736564611735_120826945869404446_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=hpQQdSIyy-UQ7kNvgHuNsID&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCPfx7Fwb4K4QC8u7AaVp-ECGbGjiVxjWEodcIFRX7UiQ&oe=670A67F2"}, "display_name": "Radial-G: Proteus", "keywords": ["radialg", "proteus", "radial", "racing", "things3d"], "long_description": "Radial-G: Proteus is a futuristic arcade racer for the VR generation! Climb into the cockpit of a gravity-defying race craft and tear up the tubular tracks as battle commences. Radial-G delivers full immersion racing featuring gut-wrenching twists, jumps, splits and unique inverted racing.\n\nFeaturing:\n- 8 modes including combat, elimination & championship\n- 9 racetracks\n- Kicking electronic soundtrack\n- Single player career mode\n- 4 unlockable ships\n- 3 speed classes\n- Achievements & leaderboards\n\nOMEGA Update \u2013 Now Live:\nBattle a giant mechanoid boss on a signature Radial-G track - avoid an array of attacks and deliver your own knock-out blows.  \n- New boss-fight game-mode with 3 difficulty tiers\n- Additional racetrack \n- Expanded single player campaign\n- 3 more unlockable ships\n\nThe Omega update delivers performance improvements, specifically within the top two difficulty tiers (X-II and X-III) plus visual improvements within the ship cockpits and additional audio elements.", "short_description": "Radial-G: Proteus is a futuristic arcade racer for the VR generation! Climb into the cockpit of a gravity-defying race craft and tear up the tubular tracks as battle commences. Radial-G delivers full immersion racing featuring gut-wrenching twists, jumps, splits and unique inverted racing."